@startuml
title BP-13 - Penalty and Grace Period Configuration

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Finance Officer|
start
:Create late payment policy;
:Define due date basis;
:Define grace period;
:Define penalty amount or percentage;

|Payment Rule Engine|
:Validate grace period is not negative;
:Validate penalty value;
:Validate applicable products;

if (Penalty rule valid?) then (Yes)
  :Save penalty and grace period policy;
else (No)
  :Return validation error;
  stop
endif

|Billing Engine|
:Check overdue obligations;
if (Grace period exceeded?) then (Yes)
  :Apply penalty rule;
  :Update outstanding obligation or create adjustment;
else (No)
  :Do not apply penalty yet;
endif

|Notification Engine|
:Send overdue reminder if configured;
stop

note right
Current MVP has due dates and outstanding status.
Dedicated penalty calculation is future scope.
end note
@enduml
